{"tid":1507493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東區醫院逾 700 名醫護實名聯署　斥警方妨礙人道救援　剝奪示威者人權","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:50:59.000Z","uid":53379,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"870dd4258ab1b74b5d9cd8cfa30f573e4cd4888a","tid":1507493,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:27:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東區醫院逾 700 名醫護實名聯署　斥警方妨礙人道救援　剝奪示威者人權</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tungkui_mGRew_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftungkui_mGRew_1200x0.png&h=febf6fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東區醫院有超過700名醫護人員實名聯署，要求政府回應五大訴求。他們又批評警方連日多次妨礙人道救援，阻礙救護車進入集會範圍，是嚴重剝奪示威者基本人權。他們抗議警方任意進入醫院範圍，令病人以及醫護人員感到人身安全受威脅。<br />\n<br />\n東區醫院超過700名醫護聯署，包括有醫生、護士、化驗師放射師、物理治療師、文員等。他們斥政府放縱警方濫權及使用暴力，令示威者以至普羅市民身受嚴重傷害，更多次妨害傷者求治。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，警方迄今使用接近2000發催淚彈，有市民受催淚煙影響相繼出現呼吸系統、腸道及皮膚病狀，老人及小孩尤為嚴重。有指警方於行動中曾經使用過期催淚彈，警方至今未有否認。專家指出過期催淚彈發射後經加熱有機會釋出山埃、光氣等有毒氣體，難以估計其對市民健康影響。<br />\n<br />\n他們批評警方多次妨礙人道救援工作，「警察以示威者被捕為由，阻礙救護車進入集會範圍，嚴重剝奪示威者基本人權。警方亦多次攻擊在場已表明身份的醫療人員並將其拘捕，此舉不但令救援工作受阻，亦已違反國際人權法。」聲明又指有警員一度試圖進入醫院急症室搜捕懷疑示威者，「我們嚴正抗議警方任意進入醫院範圍，令病人以及醫護人員感到人身安全受威脅，我們亦呼籲警方勿以執法為由阻礙人道救援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%BE-700-%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4-%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A/?fbclid=IwAR0RIZEWdppdgXx3V2jlEfq3RHscjT390mwco80lnl3WLsqnT5ILqZbAo8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2580%25BE-700-%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2595%2591%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0RIZEWdppdgXx3V2jlEfq3RHscjT390mwco80lnl3WLsqnT5ILqZbAo8Y&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=8eb928e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2580%25BE-700-%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2595%2591%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0RIZEWdppdgXx3V2jlEfq3RHscjT390mwco80lnl3WLsqnT5ILqZbAo8Y&h=5f37e226\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%BE-700-%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4-%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A/?fbclid=IwAR0RIZEWdppdgXx3V2jlEfq3RHscjT390mwco80lnl3WLsqnT5ILqZbAo8Y</a>"},{"pid":"481da42491b10ef6585b77555957760a22641910","tid":1507493,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=6461f415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"b2b40fd13fb4b0651b8e18d